{"id":430961,"date":[{"year":1962,"month":5,"day":24}],"page":"4","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"笔会","column":"","genre":"","count":"109","ytitle":"","mtitle":"月(外一首)","ftitle":"","authors":["屠岸"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"屠岸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天上是一片深蓝，云海茫茫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只有一个孤独的月亮在彷徨；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地上有多少河流，多少池塘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就有多少个月亮的脸庞在发光。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是大地热爱着月亮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在人间描绘她无数美丽的肖象；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还是月亮热爱着人间，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叫万千化身投入大地的胸膛?"}]}